{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"meets7to1","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb"},{"text":" { ","kind":"text"},{"text":"get","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" }","kind":"text"}],"languages":["swift"]}]}],"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsfoundations\/oudswcag21ratio\/meets7to1"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations","doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations\/OUDSWCAG21Ratio"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations\/OUDSWCAG21Ratio\/meets7to1","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"metadata":{"symbolKind":"property","externalID":"s:15OUDSFoundations15OUDSWCAG21RatioV9meets7to1Sbvp","role":"symbol","title":"meets7to1","roleHeading":"Instance Property","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"meets7to1","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb"}],"modules":[{"name":"Foundations"}]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"If the computed contrast ratio between two given colors meets the 7:1 requirement"}],"references":{"doc://OUDSFoundations/documentation/OUDSFoundations/OUDSWCAG21Ratio":{"fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSWCAG21Ratio","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSWCAG21Ratio","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Some countries set up new laws so as to force companies to have a better accessibility of their digital services."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This is for example the case for France with the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/accessibilite.numerique.gouv.fr","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"also named “RGAA”."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The WCAG specifications, for AA level, defines a contrast ratio of 4.5:1 for textual elements (i.e. texts), and 3:1 for non-textual elements (i.e. link’s chevron)."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"However it is higly recommended for mobile devices to reach AAA level because of the screen sizes and luminosity issues, i.e. 7:1 for textual"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and 4.5:1 for non-textual elements."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This utility helps to define whether a set of contrast ratio matches AA and AAA or not."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"See for example "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/system.design.orange.com\/0c1af118d\/p\/2531b9-accessibility-compliance","isActive":true}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsfoundations\/oudswcag21ratio","role":"symbol","title":"OUDSWCAG21Ratio","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations\/OUDSWCAG21Ratio"},"doc://OUDSFoundations/documentation/OUDSFoundations":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations","title":"Foundations","role":"collection","images":[{"identifier":"ic_layers.png","type":"icon"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsfoundations","abstract":[{"text":"Contains a set of helpers and extensions shared for higher level targets.","type":"text"}]},"https://system.design.orange.com/0c1af118d/p/2531b9-accessibility-compliance":{"type":"link","titleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"the following guidelines"}],"title":"the following guidelines","identifier":"https:\/\/system.design.orange.com\/0c1af118d\/p\/2531b9-accessibility-compliance","url":"https:\/\/system.design.orange.com\/0c1af118d\/p\/2531b